00:13:48.879 --> 00:13:49.920
That was pretty exciting.

00:13:49.920 --> 00:13:53.430
I also want to switch over
to talking about monetization

00:13:53.430 --> 00:13:54.680
and also get us back on time.

00:13:54.680 --> 00:13:56.638
We've got a clicker, and
