00:17:16.440 --> 00:17:18.740
You can see from here
that it fits very well

00:17:18.740 --> 00:17:20.470
within the visual
style of the game

00:17:20.470 --> 00:17:23.569
and shows you how you can easily
integrate it into, for example,

00:17:23.569 --> 00:17:24.650
user interfaces.

00:17:24.650 --> 00:17:27.000
So again, it looks
like it belongs.

00:17:27.000 --> 00:17:28.890
Native Ads can take
the form of an app

00:17:28.890 --> 00:17:31.580
install or promoting
new content.

00:17:31.580 --> 00:17:33.560
And it pulls from our
network of over a million

00:17:33.560 --> 00:17:35.220
Google advertisers.

00:17:35.220 --> 00:17:37.740
Your game simply just gets
the metadata for the ad.

00:17:37.740 --> 00:17:41.750
