icon, even the store rating.

00:17:41.750 --> 00:17:43.860
And you decide how to
render it in your game,

00:17:43.860 --> 00:17:45.420
using Google Guidelines.

00:17:45.420 --> 00:17:48.230
And this is available
for Android and iOS.

00:17:48.230 --> 00:17:50.580
It's in limited beta
right now, but it's one

00:17:50.580 --> 00:17:55.360
that we're excited
to expand in 2015.

