And these pay TV
operators that you

00:18:48.170 --> 00:18:51.080
see here are switching
their entire platform

00:18:51.080 --> 00:18:55.450
to set-top boxes using
Android TV, as well.

00:18:55.450 --> 00:18:58.240
Bringing your game to Android
TV is very straightforward.

00:18:58.240 --> 00:19:01.150
