allows the instances

00:20:05.280 --> 00:20:07.710
of games running on
phones, tablets, and TVs

00:20:07.710 --> 00:20:10.540
to find each other on
the same Wi-Fi network.

00:20:10.540 --> 00:20:13.200
We then create a peer-to-peer
network between them,

00:20:13.200 --> 00:20:15.890
and you can communicate
between those devices.

00:20:15.890 --> 00:20:19.440
And this allows you to create
truly amazing local multiplayer

00:20:19.440 --> 00:20:23.120
and second screen devices with
devices sitting in your pocket.

